data.description: WELCOME..Step into this charmingly renovated East Point residence and experience the warmth of homecoming! As you enter through the front door, you'll be greeted by the gleaming hardwood floors, a stunning tiled fireplace, and an abundance of natural light that bathes the entire space. Embrace your inner culinary artist in the kitchen, equipped with brand-new stainless-steel appliances and a beautifully tiled backsplash. At the end of a long day, retreat to your luxurious owner's suite, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a rejuvenating en suite bathroom. Indulge in relaxation within the expansive soaker tub, a floor-to-ceiling tiled shower, and a generously-sized double vanity. Ample storage is at your disposal, thanks to the presence of two additional guest rooms and a full daylight basement. This home offers incredible potential, featuring a stand-up attic that is ready to be transformed to your liking, as well as two separate exterior entrances in the basement, making it ideal for an in-law suite or income-generating space. Plus, you can rest easy knowing that the home boasts new HVAC, electrical, and plumbing systems, and the roof is just two years old. Conveniently located, you'll be just minutes away from the airport, Downtown East Point, Tyler Perry Studios, major highways, shopping centers, dining establishments, and much more. Welcome to your new home!
